  "remarks": "\nDobrolet was a subsidiary of a Russian state-owned airline. Since the annexation of Crimea Dobrolet exclusively operated flights between Moscow and Simferopol. It therefore facilitated the integration of the annexed Autonomous Republic of Crimea into the Russian Federation and undermines Ukrainian sovereignty and territorial integrity The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
